Notes: The 'row_id' serves as a unique identifier for each record, making 'hasIdentifier' the most semantically appropriate property.
Patient information relates directly to the main problem condition, making this path appropriate for linking patient data.
Diagnosis codes are represented via the 'hasCode' property, linking to a Code entity that captures coding details.
The 'created_at' timestamp naturally maps to the 'hasDateTime' property with datatype dateTime.
Organizational code is related to administrative aspects, hence linked via 'hasAdministrativeCase'.
Organization name is part of administrative data, linked via 'hasAdministrativeCase'.
